The following people have helped make Amara possible:

* Fellow core 4Suite developers Mike Olson, Jeremy Kloth, Mike Brown and Chimezie Ogbuji for the foundation on which Amara is built
* Norm Walsh and Eric van der Vlist for useful discussion of namespace handling in Amara
* Tom Lazar and Luis Miguel Morillas for steady feedback on the mutation API
* Jamie Norrish for converting the documentation from AkaraML to markdown, alongside content and editing updates

